200 seconds he said adding that the employees are being denied 
sick leave 
ssa said it reduced the busy signal rate in march partly through 
the use of a system to reroute calls during peak calling times 
as we have identified problems and gained experience with the 
system we have been able to modify our procedures along the way in 
order to improve our performance hardy told the panel 
this will be the largest 800number in the world she said 
in a prepared text i want it to be the best 
a survey conducted by ssa in february found that 84 percent of 
callers interviewed were satisfied with the phone service and 98 
percent thought they had been treated courteously the 
administration said 
