the panels current deliberations are not unlike those of a 
grand jury 
finding reason to believe that rules have been violated 
would be equivalent to an indictment of wright the speaker would 
then have a chance to defend himself in a disciplinary hearing the 
equivalent of a trial 
wright reported his wifes employment with fort worth developer 
george mallick on his financial disclosure forms as salary for her 
work but the ethics panels outside counsel richard phelan 
argued that the salary amounted to a gift because mrs wright did 
little work in exchange for it 
